nodes.text: 397-10B was a cleaning droid inside Besadii casino's underground facility on Katalla. During Anakin Skywalker and Ahsoka Tano's mission to destroy the casino vault, 397-10B was alerted to their presence when he found an unexplained piece of debris in one of the tunnels of the facility.
"The Professional!"—Star Wars: The Clone Wars Comic UK 6.12 (First appearance)
